  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: High Cost Tariff Excluded Device - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_high_cost_tariff_excluded_device">High Cost Tariff Excluded Device</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_medical_device">MEDICAL DEVICE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_high_cost_tariff_excluded_device">High Cost Tariff Excluded Device</xref>
 is an expensive 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_medical_device">MEDICAL DEVICE</xref>
 that is excluded from the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/national_tariff_payment_system.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">National_Tariff_Payment_System</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
For a complete list of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_high_cost_tariff_excluded_device">High Cost Tariff Excluded Devices</xref>
, see the annual National Prices and National Tariff Workbook in the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/national_tariff_payment_system.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">National_Tariff_Payment_System</xref>
 section on the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_improvement">NHS Improvement</xref>
 website at 
    <xref href="https://improvement.nhs.uk/resources/developing-the-national-tariff/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Developing the national tariff</xref>
.  </p>

